'''Monofilament''' was a fine, durable thread used for many purposes. Monofilament can refer to:
*[[Cocooned monofilament]]
*[[Computational monofilament]]
*[[Mono-filament trace-wire]]
*[[Monofilament cable]], also known as monofilament line
*[[Monofilament chain]]
*[[Monofilament fiber]]
*[[Monofilament fishing line]]
*[[Monofilament mesh]]
*[[Monofilament net]]
*[[Monofilament wire]]
*[[Monofilament screen guard|Novaplex Monofilament Screen Guard]]

